title: BRIEF-Anevia entered into strategic partnership agreement with Digisoft.tv
text:
BRIEF-Anevia entered into strategic partnership agreement with Digisoft.tv Sept 11 
* Entered into a strategic partnership agreement with Digisoft.tv 
* Focus of partnership will be integration of viamotion infinite into Digisoft.tv's "castcatcher" HDMI product range 
Source text: bit.ly/1K2cDkK Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
